      <title>两年内首艘报废超级油轮是一艘暗色船</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-27/first-supertanker-to-be-scrapped-in-two-years-is-a-dark-ship</link>
      <description><![CDATA[“阿莫尔”号是一艘悬挂喀麦隆国旗的油轮，已知曾运输过伊朗石油，它已成为两年多来第一艘登记拆解的超级油轮，这一迹象表明，对运输制裁原油的船只的审查越来越严格，给运营商带来了更大压力。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-27/first-supertanker-to-be-scrapped-in-two-years-is-a-dark-ship</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 27 Dec 2024 10:07:51 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>德国总统解散议会并宣布 2 月 23 日举行选举</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-27/german-president-dissolves-parliament-and-calls-feb-23-election</link>
      <description><![CDATA[德国总统弗兰克-瓦尔特·施泰因迈尔解散了议会，并将该国提前大选定于 2 月 23 日举行，正式批准了总理奥拉夫·朔尔茨在上个月退出执政联盟后提出的时间表。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-27/german-president-dissolves-parliament-and-calls-feb-23-election</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 27 Dec 2024 10:01:26 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>卢拉新任党魁誓言放弃自身观点，支持哈达德计划</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-27/lula-s-pt-leader-lindbergh-vows-to-set-aside-own-views-to-back-haddad-s-plan</link>
      <description><![CDATA[巴西众议院执政党即将上任的领导人承诺放弃其党派所持的较为激进的观点，转而支持财政部长费尔南多·阿达德 (Fernando Haddad) 的经济议程，他认为该议程的成功对于总统路易斯·伊纳西奥·卢拉·达席尔瓦 (Luiz Inacio Lula da Silva) 在 2026 年的连任至关重要。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-27/lula-s-pt-leader-lindbergh-vows-to-set-aside-own-views-to-back-haddad-s-plan</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 27 Dec 2024 10:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>乌克兰向叙利亚运送500吨面粉作为人道主义援助</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-27/ukraine-ships-500-tons-of-flour-to-syria-as-humanitarian-aid</link>
      <description><![CDATA[乌克兰向叙利亚提供了 500 吨面粉作为人道主义援助，寻求在俄罗斯支持的叙利亚政府倒台后与叙利亚建立联系。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-27/ukraine-ships-500-tons-of-flour-to-syria-as-humanitarian-aid</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 27 Dec 2024 09:45:14 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
