      <title>组织称肯尼亚绑架异见人士是为了压制批评者</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-27/dissident-abductions-in-kenya-is-bid-to-mute-critics-group-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[肯尼亚人权活动人士称，过去 10 天内至少有 7 名批评政府的人被绑架，他们声称绑架行动旨在压制异议。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-27/dissident-abductions-in-kenya-is-bid-to-mute-critics-group-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 27 Dec 2024 09:07:53 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
