      <title>马来西亚安瓦尔认为与他信的关系带来宝贵机遇</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-27/malaysia-s-anwar-sees-invaluable-opportunity-from-thaksin-ties</link>
      <description><![CDATA[马来西亚总理安瓦尔·易卜拉欣表示，泰国前领导人他信·西那瓦的专业知识将使马来西亚在明年担任东盟主席国的准备中受益。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-27/malaysia-s-anwar-sees-invaluable-opportunity-from-thaksin-ties</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 27 Dec 2024 07:57:05 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>危机加深 韩国两周内弹劾两位领导人</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-27/south-korea-s-parliament-passes-vote-to-impeach-acting-president</link>
      <description><![CDATA[韩国议会弹劾了代理总统韩德洙，这对于政府而言又是一个沉重的打击。不到两周前，总统尹锡烈因发布短暂的戒严令而被停职。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-27/south-korea-s-parliament-passes-vote-to-impeach-acting-president</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 27 Dec 2024 07:39:38 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
