      <title>据韩联社报道，韩国检察机关起诉前国防部长金某</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-27/south-korea-prosecutors-indict-ex-defense-minister-kim-yonhap</link>
      <description><![CDATA[韩联社援引韩国检察机关特别调查部门的话称，韩国检察机关以参与总统尹锡烈宣布戒严为由，对前国防部长金容铉提起公诉。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-27/south-korea-prosecutors-indict-ex-defense-minister-kim-yonhap</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 27 Dec 2024 07:27:40 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>孟加拉国对哈西娜展开新调查，印度请求引渡</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-27/bangladesh-targets-hasina-with-new-probe-india-extradition-plea</link>
      <description><![CDATA[孟加拉国在对前被罢免领导人谢赫哈西娜的腐败调查中增加了新的指控，并向印度施压，要求将她引渡到该国接受指控，此举可能进一步加剧这两个南亚国家之间的关系紧张。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-27/bangladesh-targets-hasina-with-new-probe-india-extradition-plea</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 27 Dec 2024 07:21:15 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>泰国政府试图影响央行的计划遭遇挫折</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-27/thai-government-suffers-setback-in-bid-to-influence-central-bank</link>
      <description><![CDATA[泰国政府向泰国央行施压，要求其降低利率的努力遭遇重大挫折，泰国国务委员会办公室实际上裁定，前财政部长基迪拉特·纳拉侬 (Kittiratt Na-Ranong) 的正式提名人选不适合担任央行行长。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-27/thai-government-suffers-setback-in-bid-to-influence-central-bank</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 27 Dec 2024 04:07:45 GMT</pubDate>
